data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT! Imagine a peaceful afternoon relaxing in a hammock on your own private retreat of 10 acres! This farmhouse-style home is a short drive from the charming downtown Monroe, filled with restaurants, retail shops, the historic Dowd Center Theatre, and so much more. Easy access to Hwy 74 Bypass makes northbound trips a breeze. Fenced pastures along the private drive offer plenty of room for horses. The home is situated in the wooded part of the property, providing an extra private feel. Interior has many updates with custom styling; the oversized primary bathroom has been fully upgraded recently. The 16’x28’ screened porch connects the main living area and garage with an upstairs bonus room, nearly an additional 500 sq. ft. space; the porch is great for entertaining, rain or shine. Come see the potential!
